    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="col-span-1 py-8">
        <!-- <p class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto">
          Imagine you are a researcher whose goal is to create a map of the
          entire seabed, including all the plants and marine animals, and show
          how it has changed over time. To accomplish this, you travel around
